{"tid":1521800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Gastby 香體抹汗濕紙巾","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:10:13.000Z","uid":171668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e1d26442d5cce2c4bf35787ac1a1a2bba1329f","tid":1521800,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c61d3f94ef956b52e82637ff466c4c561ef5c46","tid":1521800,"uid":139282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"7072ef92555f2a5a83c06e12116dacb733bfcf6a","tid":1521800,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！<br />\n<br />\nBe Water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"efd0a49d96ab4c77aeb387e9e1dd2eeee176cf09","tid":1521800,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb794e81fca7c5f6b6c2fe697e0bd171c262fedd","tid":1521800,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要接送<br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路"},{"pid":"6224c981db023c8f59da77c50e4506cd78c3da3c","tid":1521800,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"就杜浩成法官作出有罪假定及煽動他人侵權之言論作出投訴（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1521682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1521682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a32b293a3afa4893693ab3b3d29900a1eb75f83a","tid":1521800,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4061251f4fcbcbb404ae7eac419a2b62b0840fd3","tid":1521800,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"濕紙巾全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ee6fb1ad2044981f830fb915d01088cb9f67